graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    DSPO -->|orchestration platform| K8s[Kubernetes/OpenShift 4.11+]
    DSPO -->|workflow engine v2| Argo[Argo Workflows 3.5.14]
    DSPO -->|workflow engine v1| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines / Tekton 1.8+]
    DSPO -->|artifact storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage]
    DSPO -->|metadata storage| DB[MySQL/MariaDB 10.3+]
    DSPO -->|authentication| OAuth[OAuth Proxy v4.12+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    DSPO -.->|service mesh optional| Envoy[Envoy Proxy / OSSM 2.x]
    DSPO -.->|certificates optional| CertManager[cert-manager 1.13+]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    DSPO -->|external access| Route[OpenShift Route]
    DSPO -.->|optional mTLS| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh / Istio]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|embeds UI| DSPO
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|can deploy| KServe[KServe]
    Pipelines -->|can deploy| Ray[Ray]
    Pipelines -->|can deploy| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving]

    DSPO -->|manages| Pipelines

    %% External Services
    DSPO -->|pulls images| Registry[Container Registry]
    DSPO -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]

    %% Monitoring
    DSPO -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]

